headline: Rodents on the run: Orkin Canada releases 2025 list of Rattiest Cities
summary: Orkin Canada’s annual national “Rattiest Cities” list is out!MISSISSAUGA, Ontario, Dec. 09, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Orkin Canada has released its annual list of the top 25 “rattiest” cities in Canada, with Toronto once again claiming the top spot.
